No. D-2515. In the Matter of Discipline of Peter Michael Callegary. 562 U.S. 811, 131 S. Ct. 400,

178 L. Ed. 2d 266,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7608. October 4, 2010.

Peter Michael Calle-gary, of Towson, Maryland, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
